<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">11倍速算法，11乘某数,只要将其数扩大10倍,再加上某数即为其积.其口诀是：十一乘作十来算，再将某数添。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×11=a×10+a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">36×11=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 36×11</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=36×10+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=360+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=396</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>